<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="success-container">
          <div class="success-icon">‚úì</div>
          
          <h1 style="color: #10b981; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            ITR Filed Successfully!
          </h1>
          <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 1.1rem;">
            Your Income Tax Return has been submitted successfully
          </p>
          
          <div class="ack-number">
            <h3>Acknowledgement Number</h3>
            <div class="number"><%= acknowledgement.number %></div>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.9rem;">
              Filed on: <%= acknowledgement.timestamp.toLocaleString('en-IN') %>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="alert alert-info" style="text-align: left; margin: 2rem auto; max-width: 600px;">
            <strong>üìã Next Steps:</strong><br><br>
            1. <strong>Download ITR-V:</strong> Click the button below to download your acknowledgement<br>
            2. <strong>Verify Your Return:</strong> Complete e-Verification within 120 days using:<br>
               &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;‚Ä¢ Aadhaar OTP<br>
               &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;‚Ä¢ Net Banking<br>
               &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;‚Ä¢ Bank Account Number (EVC)<br>
               &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;‚Ä¢ Or send signed ITR-V to CPC Bangalore<br>
            3. <strong>Track Status:</strong> Monitor your return processing status on the portal
          </div>
          
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="/download-itr-v" class="btn btn-success" style="text-decoration: none;">
              üì• Download ITR-V
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="text-decoration: none;">
              ‚úì e-Verify Now
            </a>
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary" style="text-decoration: none;">
              ‚Üê Back to Dashboard
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <h3 style="color: #1e3a8a; margin-bottom: 1rem;">üìä Filing Summary</h3>
            <table class="table" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Assessment Year:</strong></td>
                <td><%= acknowledgement.assessmentYear %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>ITR Form:</strong></td>
                <td><%= acknowledgement.itrType %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>PAN:</strong></td>
                <td><%= user.pan %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Name:</strong></td>
                <td><%= user.name %></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Filing Date:</strong></td>
                <td><%= acknowledgement.timestamp.toLocaleDateString('en-IN') %></td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
          
          <div class="alert alert-warning" style="margin-top: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> This acknowledgement does NOT mean your return is processed or refund is approved. 
            It only confirms that your return has been received. Processing typically takes 2-3 weeks after e-Verification.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  
  <script>
    // Confetti animation on success (optional but nice touch)
    window.addEventListener('load', function() {
      console.log('üéâ ITR Filed Successfully!');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
